      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:50:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行预计今年将出现降息条件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/bank-of-canada-expects-rate-cut-conditions-to-emerge-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行官员表示，如果经济发展符合他们的预测，他们今年可能会开始降息，但表示春季房地产反弹将使通胀形势复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/bank-of-canada-expects-rate-cut-conditions-to-emerge-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:30:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
